***REMOVED*** Remote Mac configuration for Termux SSH scripts
***REMOVED*** Copy this file to remote_env and edit with your values:
***REMOVED***   cp remote_env.example remote_env
***REMOVED***
***REMOVED*** Prerequisites:
***REMOVED***   - Tailscale on both Mac and Android
***REMOVED***   - macOS Remote Login enabled (System Settings > General > Sharing > Remote Login)
***REMOVED***   - SSH key generated in Termux: ssh-keygen -t ed25519
***REMOVED***   - Public key added to Mac: ~/.ssh/authorized_keys

***REMOVED*** Mac SSH connection (Tailscale IP or MagicDNS hostname)
MAC_SSH_HOST=
MAC_SSH_USER=

***REMOVED*** Repo path on Mac (use quotes to prevent local ~ expansion)
MAC_REPO_DIR='~/dev/scanium'

***REMOVED*** Phone storage paths (after running termux-setup-storage)
PHONE_DOWNLOADS_DIR=~/storage/downloads
PHONE_ARTIFACT_DIR=$PHONE_DOWNLOADS_DIR/scanium-ci
PHONE_APK_DIR=$PHONE_DOWNLOADS_DIR/scanium-apk
